            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;This looks like a cut and paste without reference&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/165495/casebash&quot; title=&quot;108,538 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Casebash&lt;/a&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-date&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;comment-link&quot; href=&quot;#comment2752866_2381788&quot;&gt;&lt;span title=&quot;2010-04-28 00:06:41Z, License: CC BY-SA 2.5&quot; class=&quot;relativetime-clean&quot;&gt;Apr 28, 2010 at 0:06&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;Multiple Copy/Paste of files and name refactoring lead to the same issue, despite all file names and contents were Ok. Cleaning the project, deleting R.java manually and all the import headers, then rebuilding these import headers (still with CTRL+ SHIFT + O) worked fine.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/461212/hornetbzz&quot; title=&quot;8,852 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;hornetbzz&lt;/a&gt;
